com.google.api.ads.dfp.v201306

Class ProposalLineItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.ads.dfp.v201306.ProposalLineItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ProposalLineItem
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A ProposalLineItem is an instance of sales Product. It belongs to a Proposal and is created according to a Product and RateCard. When the proposal is turned into an Order, this object is turned into a LineItem.
    See Also:

        deliveryData * Delivery data provides the number of clicks or impressions delivered for the LineItem generated from this proposal line item in the last 7 days. This attribute is readonly and is populated by Google. This will be null if the delivery data cannot be computed due to one of the following reasons:
        1. The proposal line item has not pushed to DFP.
